text: Oranzherei () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Oranzhereininsky Selsoviet in Ikryaninsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 4,473 as of 2010. There are 23 streets. == Geography == It is located 80 km south-west from Astrakhan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ikryaninsky District
title: Oranzherei
